metadata.name: Dancing Baby In Colors
metadata.description:
Introduction:

The "Dancing Baby," an early internet meme from 1996, is recognized as one of the first viral memes, marking the birth of the meme culture we know today.

To honor the "Dancing Baby's" 27th birthday and its journey into the Metaverse, on April 27, 2023, Anna Dart is releasing an AI art version of the iconic meme, showcasing the collaboration between human and machine through mesmerizing color blends. The Metaverse fosters collaboration and creativity, and the "Dancing Baby" has always been a symbol of innovation and decentralization.

About the artist:

Anna Dart, an awarded artist and futurist with over 10 years of painting experience, is known for her minimalist style art that exhibits a powerful expressiveness reflecting digital humanism.
